assert (0 == 3)

 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7d55f86df580> = [[1, -95], [1, -95, 1], [-95, 1], [-95, 1, -95], [1, -95], [1, -95, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -9025 == -95
 +  where -9025 = <built-in function prod>([-5, -19, -95])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
